positions.description:
Responsible for the development and execution of software product lifecycle, go-to-market and business development strategies enabling growth in developer communities and monetizing installed base users.

Specific responsibility for MySQL big data & Hadoop integration, NoSQL APIs, cloud and High Availability (HA) distributed database offerings.

Accomplishments
− Established MySQL as the leading relational database for Big Data platforms by defining and launching Hadoop integration features and NoSQL APIs. Independent estimates now size MySQL as commanding an 80% share of RDBMS’ integrated with Hadoop;

− Created the MySQL Web Reference Architecture program to support product adoption in new mobile and cloud services;

− Developed a high-volume content marketing engine to accelerate sales-cycles through lead generation and automated qualification;

− Released multiple MySQL solution offerings with open source projects and commercial ISVs, including joint marketing, sales and engineering initiatives.
